summary: “I used to be embarrassed because I was just a comic-book writer while other people were building bridges or going on to medical...
body:
“I used to be embarrassed because I was just a comic-book writer while other people were building bridges or going on to medical careers. And then I began to realize: entertainment is one of the most important things in people’s lives. Without it they might go off the deep end. I feel that if you’re able to entertain people, you’re doing a good thing.”

~ Stan Lee , December 28 1922 - November 12 2018

Excelsior!

summary: Stan Lee nos games: Relembre as aparições do lendário quadrinista nos jogos da Marvel
title: Stan Lee nos games: Relembre as aparições do lendário quadrinista nos jogos da Marvel
body:
Descanse em paz, mestre Stan Lee :( Para celebrar a memória do criador de grandes personagens como o Homem-Aranha, reunimos as aparições do quadrinista no mundo dos games.

Na tarde desta segunda-feira, 12, o site TMZ trouxe uma notícia triste para os amantes da cultura pop: Stan Lee, um dos caras mais influentes da história do mundo geek, faleceu aos 95 anos. Um dos principais nomes por trás da Marvel e de personagens amados como o Homem de Ferro, Doutor  Estranho e Homem-Aranha, o quadrinista moldou o imaginário de muitas crianças e adolescentes desde os anos 60.

He was truly the father of Marvel, and he will be missed greatly by so many people. Rest easy, Mr. Stan. You have inspired me and so many others. Thank you.
